-- Sri Lanka May Sell Shares, List Shell Subsidiary on Colombo Stock Exchange
-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e   a n d   A s a n t h a   S i r i m a n n e
-- 2010-10-07T06:12:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-07/sri-lanka-may-sell-shares-list-shell-subsidiary-on-colombo-stock-exchange.html
Sri Lanka may sell shares in the
local unit of Royal Dutch Shell Plc to the public and list it
on the Colombo Stock Exchange, Cabinet Spokesman Keheliya
Rambukwella told reporters in the capital today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
